entry.string: # Cleanup on error docker stop maven-build-temp 2>/dev/null || true docker rm maven-build-temp 2>/dev/null || true
Build failed: script returned exit code 1

# Stop and remove any leftover containers for container in maven-build-temp maven-package-temp maven-sonar-temp; do docker stop $container 2>/dev/null || echo "Container $container not running" docker rm $container 2>/dev/null || echo "Container $container not found" done
# Generic cleanup for any maven containers docker ps -aq --filter "name=maven-" | xargs -r docker stop 2>/dev/null || echo "No maven containers to stop" docker ps -aq --filter "name=maven-" | xargs -r docker rm -f 2>/dev/null || echo "No maven containers to clean"
